{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"4qfbc1w17nlx6arb6djhxx2","title":"Sync-and-Send","desc":"","updated":1670569908647,"created":1670568874758,"custom":{},"fname":"programing.rust.Concurrency.Sync-and-Send","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"dd212778a201937f2fe05016bf7976e4","links":[],"anchors":{"sync-and-send-traits":{"type":"header","text":"Sync and Send Traits","value":"sync-and-send-traits","line":7,"column":0,"depth":1},"send---transfering-ownership-between-threads":{"type":"header","text":"Send - Transfering ownership between threads","value":"send---transfering-ownership-between-threads","line":11,"column":0,"depth":2},"sync---allowing-access-from-multiple-threads":{"type":"header","text":"Sync - Allowing access from multiple threads","value":"sync---allowing-access-from-multiple-threads","line":17,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"ikux7kdtkym0buow03rwec7","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"sync-and-send\">Sync-and-Send<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#sync-and-send\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"sync-and-send-traits\">Sync and Send Traits<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#sync-and-send-traits\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://doc.rust-lang.org/book/ch16-04-extensible-concurrency-sync-and-send.html\">https://doc.rust-lang.org/book/ch16-04-extensible-concurrency-sync-and-send.html</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"send---transfering-ownership-between-threads\">Send - Transfering ownership between threads<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#send---transfering-ownership-between-threads\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>The <code>Send</code> <em>marker trait</em> indicates that ownership of values of the type implementing it can be <strong>transfered between threads</strong>.</li>\n<li>Any type composed entirely of <code>Send</code> types is automatically marked as <code>Send</code></li>\n<li>Almost all primitive types are <code>Send</code> (aside from raw pointers)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"sync---allowing-access-from-multiple-threads\">Sync - Allowing access from multiple threads<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#sync---allowing-access-from-multiple-threads\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>The <code>Sync</code> <em>market trait</em> indicates that it is safe for the type implementing it to be <strong>referenced from multiple threads</strong>.</li>\n<li>Any type <code>T</code> is <code>Sync</code> if <code>&#x26;T</code> (immutable reference) is <code>Send</code></li>\n<li>Primitive types are <code>Sync</code></li>\n<li>Types composed entirely of types that are <code>Sync</code> are also <code>Sync</code></li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Implementing Send &#x26; Sync manually is Unsafe</p>\n</blockquote>","noteIndex":{"id":"xfkxbponh0sohobo6pual15","title":"Root","desc":"","updated":1668137379975,"created":1663481872547,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"cb44915142ec96bef8f764f3dc90389e","links":[],"anchors":{"welcome-to-my-page":{"type":"header","text":"Welcome to my page","value":"welcome-to-my-page","line":7,"column":0,"depth":1},"contacts":{"type":"header","text":"Contacts","value":"contacts","line":12,"column":0,"depth":2},"dendron":{"type":"header","text":"Dendron","value":"dendron","line":18,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["u5a2e2vvfn3x7k0shuvmb1b","qw8y69zxn8wr7tzz4gtcrrv","q7qw45jglqwmynary64q67c","6wjqcjgkrpeqtmzb1o8o1q8","3ervbn5we7t8v2l2vwtx847","4qi2z0z9fquupbd651xausx","sencgim78q74o1zuyvy1vz7","ue4oml1si982t3mmbthyxi9","zrogwjgtze8ne5joqpz8ty9","oesia0lbzh03fsoy124ck0k","el3p9zjue6h3b6zsl9oejkt","t5grkmcwvu4nl43igsj4gxz"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"# Welcome to my page\n\n- This is a place where I write my knowledge in both Vietnamese and English.\n- Please feel free to correct me if there is anything not right.\n\n## Contacts\n\n- [Github](ht